data.description: Welcome to your Home Sweet Home!  This conveniently located 4 Bedroom 2.5 Bath, two-story residence, on a generous corner lot in the very popular Millstone Crossing has lots of recent updates making it the perfect choice. The main floor welcomes you with a spacious layout connecting the kitchen, breakfast area, and great room, creating a haven for family gatherings and entertaining. The kitchen, the heart of every home, features ample cabinetry, counter space, and a convenient island and breakfast area. The oversized great room a a true focal point of the home promotes a sense of togetherness, whether you're hosting a lively get-together or simply relaxing with loved ones. Large windows frame views of the fenced backyard creating an openness and connecting to the outdoors.  Adjacent to the kitchen you will find the dining room, an elegant setting for every occasion.  Need a quiet space to work from home, do school work or enjoy a hobby? Look no further as this home boasts a dedicated office/flex space, allowing you to stay focused and productive without sacrificing comfort. The thoughtful design with built in shelving ensures the space is both functional and aesthetically pleasing. The upstairs layout is a testament to the careful consideration put into every detail of this home. Bedrooms are just steps away, making the morning rush seamless and stress-free. Each bedroom is generously sized offering plenty of space for relaxation and personalization. The shared bath boasts a double vanity, providing ample space for everyone's morning routine. For added functionality, this bathroom is designed with a separate shower room, offering both privacy and efficiency. It allows a harmonious blend of shared living without sacrificing individual comfort. The master suite is invitingly comfortable featuring a roomy ensuite bathroom with double vanity, garden tub, separate shower and ample closet space.  Step outside into the fenced backyard, where you'll find the perfect spot for outdoor gatherings, playtime with the kids, or simply enjoying your morning coffee in privacy. The corner lot adds an extra layer of exclusivity, providing additional green space and a sense of openness. Conveniently located near downtown Jefferson, groceries, restaurants and schools plus a short drive to I-85, this home offers not just a place to live, but a lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful property yours - Schedule a showing today and let the charm captivate you!
